task.summary: Default task
Closed items now have a line through their title.
Implemented delete item command.
Added item detail.
Added support for questions and make item status a dropdown.
Added support for activity.
Project totals table now showing correct totals and added backlog total too.
Added github integration.
Added missing files from github integration (plus other missing files)
Minor improvements to style of github messages
Test commit
Browser title now updates with number of incoming messages in brackets.
Added support for github ping event
Fixed for #OLS-1 - project summary was showing NaN% instead of 0%
Fixed bug OLS-4: publication for itemActivity was preventing item activity from downloading.
#OLS-30: Item detail shows a task that belongs to a different project and user isn't even a member!!!
Misc CSS fixes/improvements.
#OLS-8: Milestone dropdown label has a weird font
#OLS-18: On windows the scroll bars look bad - need to style them.
#OLS-10: Milestone item dropdown css bug when item is selected.
#OLS-29: Milestone detail item list show archived items.
#OLS-7: When adding new bugs, they were added to a milestone without me specifying one!
#OLS-17: Disable all the old task command features
#OLS-45: Clicking on the back/forward links is horrible!
#OLS-44: App is unusable on laptop - need to make sidebars slide in/out
#OLS-48: Browser Title notification not working properly
#OLS-49: When creating a new project, it doesn't appear in the list until a refresh
#OLS-26: Ability to rename projects
Ensured only project admins can remove project and change release settings for project.
OLS-25: Give projects different colours and show the colour in the heading so it's easier to know what project you are looking at
OLS-59: Add totals for in-test and new items
Fixed "OLS-34: Ability to change member role" and also general improvements to member list component.
Fixed "OLS-77: Get rid of NEW status" and "OLS-78: Items created in rightview filters should appear"
OLS-20: Show assignee profile image on task item
OLS-31: Add 'Items' right-view that shows all except those in backlog and an 'All Items' right-view that shows everything.
All Items right-view now doesn't show archived items.
Removed unused chart packages.
OLS-110: The message box in detail mode always shows the item ref followed by a colon at the start of the message
OLS-110: Detail mode now shows the correct icon depending on the item type and got rid of the random empty message for now.
OLS-120: In item detail mode, the first link should show the item description
Fixed bug where content was required preventing item creation.
OLS-82: Support milestone description
OLS-82: Support for milestone description. OLS-106: Order milestones so all finished milestones are at the bottom.
Increased message page size to 150 for to experiment with performance.
Updated item ordering to be based on created-at for now just to avoid all the jumping around when I make changes.
OLS-129: Support for a discussion type.
Fixed bug where scroll back/forward buttons weren't being displayed.
Fixed bug where github issue comment caused everything to blow up ;-)
OLS-123: Re-designed activity messages for all items. Need to do it for projects and members next.
